/-!
Bulgarian Mathematical Olympiad 1998, Problem 11

Let m,n be natural numbers such that

   A = ((m + 3)ⁿ + 1) / (3m)

is an integer. Prove that A is odd.
-/

namespace Bulgaria1998P11

